<!--
  Monochrome round scored-tablet glyph for the medication-reminder notification.
  A circular tablet with a horizontal score line reads unambiguously as a pill at
  status-bar size, where the previous diagonal capsule looked like a phone. The
  score is cut as a hole (evenOdd) so it stays visible after the system tints the
  silhouette solid white.
-->
